{"article_id":"ARYN78yNCtPpG9XU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett Kavanaugh listens at his Senate Judiciary Committee confirmation hearing on Capitol Hill , September 4 , 2018 .","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"( Joshua Roberts/Reuters )","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"The allegations against Brett Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"- outlined now on the record in the Washington Post by Palo Alto University professor Christine Blasey Ford -","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"are substantial and serious .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"She claims","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"that Kavanaugh knocked her down ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"groped her ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"and attempted to remove her clothes .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Here ' s the core of her story :","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"While his friend watched ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"Kavanaugh pinned her to a bed on her back","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"and groped her over her clothes ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"grinding his body against hers","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"and clumsily attempting to pull off her one-piece bathing suit and the clothing","depth":13},{"id":16,"text":"she wore over it .","depth":13},{"id":17,"text":"When she tried to scream ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"she said ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"he put his hand over her mouth .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" I thought","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"he might inadvertently kill me , \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"said Ford , now a 51-year-old research psychologist in northern California .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"\" He was trying to attack me","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"and remove my clothing. \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Ford said","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"she was able to escape","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"when Kavanaugh ' s friend and classmate at Georgetown Preparatory School , Mark Judge , jumped on top of them ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"sending all three tumbling .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"she ran from the room ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"briefly locked herself in a bathroom","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"and then fled the house .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Do not count me among those","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"who would minimize this alleged assault .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"I went to a high school","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that had more than its share of drunken parties ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and my classmates could do crazy and stupid things ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"but an act like this was beyond the pale .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"This isn ' t \" boys will be boys. \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"Actions have consequences ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and it ' s hardly unjust to tell a person","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"if he mistreated another human being like this","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"- even a long time ago -","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"he has to remain \" merely \" a judge on the D.C . Circuit Court of Appeals .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Since Kavanaugh has denied the story , however ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"the question of whether the event is so egregious","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"that it should disqualify him","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"is moot .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"At the very least ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"if the attack happened ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"he should be disqualified for lying .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Yet","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"unless all parties start telling the same story ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"there is no way","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"to know for certain","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"if this event occurred .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"We don ' t need certainty , however ,","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"to make a decision","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"on whether a man should sit on the Supreme Court .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"I have the same standard for Brett Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"as I did for Roy Moore , for Donald Trump , for Bill Clinton - or for any other politician","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"who ' s accused of misconduct .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Is it more likely than not that the allegation is true ?","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"Given the totality of the evidence ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"I believe","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"it is more likely than not that Bill Clinton committed rape and sexual harassment .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"I believe","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"it is more likely than not that Donald Trump has committed sexual assault .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"I believe","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"it is more likely than not that Roy Moore engaged in sexual misconduct with underage girls .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"But the evidence against Kavanaugh falls far short of the evidence","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"arrayed against each of these men .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"So far at least it falls far short of the evidence against virtually any other politician or celebrity","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"who has faced consequences during this # MeToo moment .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"Here ' s why :","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"First , one way","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to help test the veracity of old claims","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"is to ask whether there is any contemporaneous corroboration .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Did the accuser tell a friend or family member or anyone about the alleged assault","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"when it occurred ?","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"With Clinton , Trump , Moore , and many other politicians and celebrities , there was ample contemporaneous corroboration .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Here , there was not .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"According to the Washington Post ,","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"\" Ford said","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"she told no one of the incident in any detail until 2012 ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"when she was in couples therapy with her husband . \"","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"That ' s almost three decades of silence","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"- three decades","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"when memories can grow cloudy","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"and recollections can change .","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"But even the allegedly corroborating notes of the therapist raise a separate problem .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"They actually contradict her story on a key detail .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"According to the Post ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"\" The notes say","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"four boys were involved ,","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"a discrepancy","depth":16},{"id":98,"text":"that","depth":18},{"id":99,"text":"Ford says","depth":18},{"id":100,"text":"was an error on the therapist ' s part .","depth":17},{"id":101,"text":"Ford said","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"there were four boys at the party but only two in the room. \"","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"Nor do the notes mention Kavanaugh ' s name ,","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"even though her husband says","depth":15},{"id":105,"text":"Ford named Kavanaugh in the sessions .","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"Those are important discrepancies ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"if six years ago she told the therapist four men","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"and says two men now ,","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"that suggests","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"that her memory of the event may be suspect .","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"As a former trial lawyer , I can tell you","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"while neither notes nor memories are infallible ,","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"in a contest between contemporaneous notes and later verbal testimony about those notes , the content of the written notes usually prevails .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Juries are extremely skeptical of witnesses","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"who contradict written notes","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"- after all , the notes are taken","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"when the words are immediate","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"and there isn ' t the overwhelming pressure of a trial","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"to conform your testimony to the desired outcome .","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"At least the investigation seems somewhat manageable .","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"If there were only four boys there ,","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"who were the other two ?","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Let ' s hear from them .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"In fact , investigators should interview everyone else at the party .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Yet given all the years","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"that have passed ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"would it be possible to find anyone","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"who remembers being at that party ?","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"Would they remember any details at all ?","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"If someone saw Kavanaugh stumbling drunk at the party ,","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"that would obviously bolster Ford ' s account .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"If another attendee says ,","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"\" He was totally sober","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"and with me the whole time , \"","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"that helps Kavanaugh .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"But the odds","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"of getting details that precise","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"are long indeed ,","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"and there is always a chance","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"that a motivated classmate might lie","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"- for either person .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"Finally , there are no other allegations of sexual misconduct against Kavanaugh .","depth":6},{"id":145,"text":"If there ' s one thing","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"we ' ve seen time and again ,","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"it ' s that one allegation often triggers a cascade of additional claims .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"There seem to be precious few men","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"who engage in serious sexual misconduct just once .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"If this was the kind of behavior","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"that Kavanaugh engaged in ,","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"then look for more people to come forward .","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"If no one does , however ,","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"we ' re left with a sole claim ,","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"made by an opposing partisan","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"( Ford is an outspoken progressive ) ,","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"that Kavanaugh strenuously denies ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that lacks any contemporaneous corroboration ,","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"and that is contradicted in material respects by her therapist ' s own notes .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"That does not add up to \" more likely than not . \"","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"But these conclusions are tentative and preliminary .","depth":5},{"id":162,"text":"The next three days are crucial .","depth":6},{"id":163,"text":"We ' ll likely hear more from Ford .","depth":8},{"id":164,"text":"I expect","depth":10},{"id":165,"text":"we ' ll hear more from Kavanaugh .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"People","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"who were at the party","depth":11},{"id":168,"text":"may come forward with their own accounts .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"The news cycle is moving so fast","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"that it seems almost absurd to speculate about the state of our knowledge even 24 hours from now ,","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"but","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"if this is the core evidence","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"supporting the","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"( very serious )","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"claim against Kavanaugh ,","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"it ' s not sufficient","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"to derail the nomination of a man with an otherwise sterling record of professional excellence and personal integrity .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":355,"left":179,"right":354,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":179,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":354,"left":209,"right":353,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":181,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":180,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":180,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":208,"left":184,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":5,"right":183,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":183,"left":6,"right":182,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":182,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":9,"right":206,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":206,"left":198,"right":205,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":193,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":190,"right":192,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":190,"left":185,"right":189,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":185,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":12,"right":188,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":188,"left":13,"right":187,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":187,"left":14,"right":186,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":186,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":192,"left":191,"right":19,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":191,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":195,"right":196,